parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. This can also lead to loss of control, especially when driving on highways or steep inclines.
symptoms: or hesitates while driving; the transmission slips or hesitates to shift gears; the vehicle surges forward or backward without warning; the transmission makes unusual noises; the speedometer needle jumps or is inaccurate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission interlock system can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission interlock system fails to engage or disengage properly; the vehicle stalls or hesitates while driving; the transmission makes unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty speedometer can cause the driver to be unaware of their actual speed, leading to accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The speedometer needle jumps or is inaccurate; the speedometer fails to display the correct speed; the speedometer makes unusual noises.
